duck ! the carbine high massacre is a 1999 american black comedy crime film about a fictional school shooting . it remains to be the only accurate documentation of the victims and families of the shooters involved in the columbine high school massacre , as well as the media and police coverage of the event . released just over six months after the columbine event , it was written , produced , and directed by william hellfire and joey smack , who also starred . after the film was released , hellfire and smack were arrested for possession of weapons on school property . the film is said to have helped pay for hellfire 's legal fees .